canonical:
  title: 琵琶行
  author: 權漢功
  language: lzh
  text: 公主烏孫萬里程江州司馬淚千行後人豈解絃中趣淸夜沉沉月轉廊
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 琵琶行
  author: 權漢功
  language: lzh
  text: 公主烏孫萬里程。江州司馬淚千行。後人豈解絃中趣。淸夜沉沉月轉廊。
korean:
  title: 비파행
  author: 권한공
  language: kor
  text: |-
    공주는 오손에게 만 리 길을 떠났고
    강주사마는 천 줄기 눈물을 흘리었다
    뒷사람이 어떻게 그 비파줄 속의 뜻을 알건가
    맑은 밤은 깊어 가는데 달은 행랑에 구른다
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0240_010_0840&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 공주(公主)는 …… 떠났고 : '
    value: 한(漢)나라 공주(公主)가 오손왕(烏孫王) 곤막(昆莫)에게 시집가면서 슬픈 회포를 비파의 곡조로 탔다.
  - key: '[주-D002] 강주사마(江州司馬)는 …… 흘리었다 : '
    value: 당나라 백락천(白樂天)이 강주사마(江州司馬)로 멀리 좌천(左遷)되어 갔는데, 강상(江上)에서 여자의 비파소리를 듣고 자기의 신세를 한탄하여 눈물을 흘렸다.
english:
  title: The Pipa Song
  author: Gwon Han-gong
  language: eng
  text: |-
    The princess journeyed ten thousand miles to the Wusun lands,
    The circuit judge of Jiangzhou wept a thousand streams of tears.
    How could those who come after understand the meaning hidden in the strings?
    On this clear night, growing ever deeper, the moon rolls past the gallery.
  footnotes:
    - The opening alludes to a Han dynasty princess who was sent to marry the Wusun king, expressing her sorrow through the pipa's melody.
    - The circuit judge of Jiangzhou refers to the Tang poet Bai Juyi, who was demoted to this remote post and, upon hearing a woman's pipa performance on the riverbank, wept at the reflection of his own fate.
